node.text: #SmackDown’s newest tag team, @shotziwwe & @tegannoxwwe_, join the crew in the @wwethebump studio to discuss their recent debut on the blue brand, and new #247Champion @reginald.wwe also stops by to recap his latest win against @ronkillings1 on #wweraw.

node.title: Shotzi & Nox and Reginald join the show: WWE’s The Bump, July 28, 2021
